name: ekeybionyx
skdetail:

Developer Terms of Use
des: With this skill, dLine devices can open your access points. For example, say: "Alexa, open the front door!". You can change the display names of your access points in the ekey bionyx app. In order to be able to use this skill, it must be linked to your ekey-bionyx-account.
